                    <div style="background:#0f172a;border-radius:10px;padding:14px">
                        <div style="font-size:11px;color:#64748b;font-weight:600;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:6px">Độ nhỏ gọn (Compactness)</div>
                        <div style="display:flex;gap:16px">
